### Traffic System (working in ScarCity scene)
- `Waypoint.cs` — graph node. `nextWaypoints`, `isExit` (red gizmo), `isStop` (blue gizmo) with stopChance/minStopTime/maxStopTime. `laneID` (-1=ignored, 0=north, 1=south, 2=east, 3=west) for U-turn prevention.
- `CarAgent.cs` — follows waypoints, random speed, handles exit/stop via coroutine. Remembers last laneID to filter out U-turns at intersections.
- `CarSpawner.cs` — spawns cars at entry waypoints every spawnInterval up to maxCars, despawns at exit waypoints.

**Traffic status:** Working. Cars spawn, drive, stop at bus stop/gas station/pizza place. Waypoint network nearly complete. 4 fully-bidirectional intersections wired with laneID system.

**Intersection wiring pattern:**
```
Entry WP (laneID=N) → Center WP (laneID=-1) → Exit WPs (laneID=0/1/2/3)
```
Center points to all exits. Exit WPs never point back to center.

